The '''Exocron Combined Air-Space Fleet''' was the primary military force of the [[Exocron system/Legends|Exocron system]].

==History==
It was the successor of the [[Exocron Airfleet]], established after the ruling council obtained data on spaceflight and advanced technology. [[Supreme Admiral/Legends|Supreme Admiral]] [[Horzao Darr]] had command over the fleet, with [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Trey David]] as second-in-command. When [[Talon Karrde]] and his group of [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] landed on [[Exocron]] to visit [[Jorj Car'das]], the Exocron Combined Air-Space Fleet provided them with an escort as they landed.<ref name="Vision of the Future" />

When Talon Karrde left Exocron, he was attacked by [[Rei'Kas]]'s pirate fleet. The fleet was destroyed at the [[Battle of Exocron]] by the [[Aing-Tii/Legends|Aing-Tii Monks]] and the Exocron Combined Air-Space Fleet.<ref name="Vision of the Future" />

